<h2>June 2024 Events in Europe</h2>
<br />
<p>Planning to visit Europe this June? Here's a calendar of events, festivals, and activities to look forward to this Summer.</p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13048998/annecy_lakefestival-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.69047619047618" alt="events in europe june" data-udi="umb://media/4d5959496a254015ac74eff6ee4e90a2" /></p>
<p>If you’re thinking of travelling to Europe this summer, then we have some good news: there are plenty of exciting events happening throughout the continent! Discover the best summer events in Europe and get involved. From music festivals in Italy to food festivals in Austria, it’s time to start marking your calendar</p>
<p>Here's a list of 2023 June events in Europe that will make your summer one to remember.</p>
<h3>2023 June Events in Europe</h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Festa" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Festa">Festa del Naviglio</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Festa%20Della" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Festa Della">Festa della Republica</a> |<a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Horse" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Horse">Horse Racing at Merano Racecourse</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Vienna" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Vienna">Vienna Summer Night Concert</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Rock" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Rock">Rock in Roma</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#San" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#San">Festa di San Giovanni</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Flower" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Flower">Flower Festival</a> | <span><a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Don" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Don">Donauinselfest</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Ischia" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Ischia">Ischia Film Festival</a> | <a data-udi="umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7f27f1594a144df99778da3380f28d93}#Fete" title="June Events in Europe" data-anchor="#Fete">Fête de la Musique</a></span></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Festa"></a></p>
<h2>Festa del Naviglio </h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a>, Italy</h3>
<h3>When: <strong>1st-10th June 2024</strong></h3>
<p><img style="width: 872px; height: 468px;" src="/media/13096555/naviglio-canal-milan.jpg?width=872&amp;height=468&amp;mode=max" alt="Naviglio canal" data-udi="umb://media/54abfdde7f7d41abb3244d864d4bfc5d" /></p>
<p>The surrounding streets of the Naviglio canal in <a data-udi="umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c54eeaf670ee47ba97f163f4a1f83fa5}" title="Milan &amp; Lake Como">Milan</a> turn into a festival for folk music and dance as well as stands featuring artistic handmade crafts. The event concludes with a spectacular torch parade.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.carnifest.com/naviglio-festival-festa-del-naviglio-in-milan-2022/" target="_blank" title="Carnifest" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Festa Della"></a></p>
<h2>Festa della Repubblica </h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a>, Italy</h3>
<h3>When: 2nd<strong> June 2024</strong></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090625/adobestock_207555055-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="june events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/3e73d25087b844c692ac893f2c76383f" /></p>
<p>The Festa della Repubblica, or Republic Day, is a national holiday in <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>. It was created to commemorate the birth of the Italian Republic, with the main celebration taking place in <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a>. This is accompanied by a military parade along Fori Imperiali Road, during which a laurel crown is laid down in front of the monument dedicated to the Unknown Soldier, symbolizing all those soldiers killed in the war.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.tripsavvy.com/republic-day-festival-in-italy-1547668" target="_blank" title="Festa della Repubblica" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Vienna"></a></p>
<h2>Vienna Summer Night Concert</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/d9194f7378c74152b5986f929fcea9ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d9194f7378c74152b5986f929fcea9ab}" title="Vienna">Vienna</a>, Austria</h3>
<h3>When: 7th June 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090630/adobestock_474944143_editorial_use_only.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="june events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/0569dc59a8a74a91aa42b84b827b5c81" /></p>
<p>Vienna is the perfect setting for unique events such as The Summer Night Concert. Each year, the world-renowned Vienna Philharmonic Orchestra gives a free open-air concert in the gardens behind Schönbrunn Palace. Imagine an enormous stage standing among sculpted flower beds, lawns, and fountains. Lights illuminate the grand Palace and fireworks sparkle across the night sky as one of the world's greatest orchestras plays live.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.sommernachtskonzert.at/index_en.html" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.sommernachtskonzert.at/index_en.html" target="_blank"></a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Rock"></a></p>
<h2>Rock in Roma</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/57bc5f34b7074843b7f19f3fc6cb7ac4}" title="Rome">Rome</a>, Italy</h3>
<h3>When: 8th June - 22nd September 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090627/adobestock_221364852.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="june events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/b777417de41a4745b173227f4b574f59" /></p>
<p>Rock in Roma is a celebration of music that takes place in the Italian capital. The event draws more than 300,000 people from all over Italy and the world, who converge on its ancient streets to listen to global acts perform on huge outdoor stages, arenas, and clubs.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://rockinroma.com/" target="_blank" title="Rock in roma" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a><a rel="noopener" href="https://rockinroma.com/" target="_blank"></a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="San"></a></p>
<h2>Festa di San Giovanni</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8b79e45930f145f6b156a9152415fa9b}" title="Florence">Florence</a>, Italy</h3>
<h3>When: 20th June 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090629/adobestock_398653421.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="june events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/8efe463d4b314987bb8bac7656985fcf" /></p>
<p>The 24th of June is one of the most important days in Florence. Saint John the Baptist, the city's patron, is celebrated with a procession and fireworks. The day begins with people lighting candles and attending mass at Santa Maria de Fiore Cathedral. After another parade, guests are invited to Piazza Santa Croce to watch 54 Florentines play the Renaissance soccer game Calcio Storico in 16th-century costumes.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://rove.me/to/florence/festa-di-san-giovanni" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Flower"></a></p>
<h2>Flower Festival</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b56bdaf2399f46828fa1f01256cae753}" title="Lake Bohinj">Lake Bohinj</a>, Slovenia</h3>
<h3>When: 24th May-9th June 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13064663/_0000_wild-flower-festival.jpg?width=500&amp;height=238.69047619047618" alt="june events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/6faa966d7be0457f83fb95b4882d528b" /></p>
<p>The International Wild Flower Festival is a collection of botanical tours, events and culinary experiences celebrating the wild plants of Bohinj and the local cuisine. The festival is held annually in May and June at various locations throughout Bohinj, a region of 24 villages spanning more than 300 kilometers.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.bohinj.si/en/international-wild-flower-festival/" target="_blank"></a><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.bohinj.si/en/international-wild-flower-festival/" target="_blank" title="Flower Festival" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.bohinj.si/en/international-wild-flower-festival/" target="_blank"></a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Don"></a></p>
<h2>Donauinselfest</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/d9194f7378c74152b5986f929fcea9ab" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d9194f7378c74152b5986f929fcea9ab}" title="Vienna">Vienna</a>, Austria</h3>
<h3>When: 21st - 27th June 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090634/microsoftteams-image-2-png.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/1469e5e5ff894c508447dbe4c30eb904" /></p>
<p>The Vienna Danube Island Festival, “Donauinselfest”, is Europe’s largest open-air festival. It takes place at the end of June on the waterfront of the beautiful Blue Danube and attracts thousands of people every year. The festival is free-of-charge and features top-class national and international stars performing on eleven stages.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://donauinselfest.at/" target="_blank"></a><a rel="noopener" href="https://donauinselfest.at/" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a><a rel="noopener" href="https://donauinselfest.at/" target="_blank"></a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Ischia"></a></p>
<h2>Ischia Film Festival</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/af2f016e6c4f412b9ddb75ba9495d88f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af2f016e6c4f412b9ddb75ba9495d88f}" title="Ischia">Ischia</a>, Italy</h3>
<h3>When: 29th June - 6th July 2024</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090635/microsoftteams-image-3-png.jpg?width=500&amp;height=281.25" alt="events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/adf8ec9d8df0435aa42ff8c64f1ceab6" /></p>
<p>The 20th edition of Ischia Film Festival will take place from June 25 to July 2, 2022 on the island of Ischia in the Gulf of <a data-udi="umb://document/3f78d09ffda249fe84dca900e9fedde9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f78d09ffda249fe84dca900e9fedde9}" title="Naples" data-anchor="#">Naples</a>. The festival will be held in the evocative spaces of the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.lonelyplanet.com/italy/ischia-porto-ischia-ponte/attractions/castello-aragonese/a/poi-sig/1029510/1325026" target="_blank">Aragonese Castle</a>, with outdoor screenings and meetings with film authors.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.ischiafilmfestival.it/index.php/en/" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a><a rel="noopener" href="https://www.ischiafilmfestival.it/index.php/en/" target="_blank"></a></p>
</div>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p> </p>
<p><a name="Fete"></a></p>
<h2><span>Fête</span> de la Musique</h2>
<br />
<h3>Where: <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc}" title="Morzine">Morzine</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0}" title="Lake Annecy">Lake Annecy</a>, France</h3>
<h3>When: 21st June 2023</h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13090626/adobestock_213328042.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="events in europe" data-udi="umb://media/e6373f624fdd43bd9220a3153944bd86" /></p>
<p>The Fête de la Musique is a free music festival in <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a>. It's held on the day of the summer solstice and features thousands of free music concerts in parks, public squares, and other venues throughout France. The festival is open to amateur and professional musicians who wish to perform. There is a variety of music for every taste, from solo artists and bands to major institutions such as orchestras, operas, and choirs.</p>
<p><a rel="noopener" href="https://fetedelamusique.culture.gouv.fr//" target="_blank" class="c-btn">Find Out More</a><a rel="noopener" href="https://fetedelamusique.culture.gouv.fr//" target="_blank"></a></p>
</div>
</div>
